beer.beer_name: I Can't Believe It's Not Bacon
beer.beer_description: Lampooning your lips from the very first swig, this porker has more mystique than any flying swine. Stuffed with malt that’s smoked locally with the same wood as prize-winning bacon, this finely crafted local collaboration is a truly unique full-flavoured brew of peaty, bacony proporktions. Go on, let this ale expand your beer horizons.
